Package: Rmultifractional
Type: Package
Title: Simulation of multifractional processes and analyses of multifractional processes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andriy Olenko, Nemini Samarakoon 
Maintainer: Nemini Samarakoon <NWijesingheS@ltu.edu.au> 
Description: Simulation of the Guassian Haar Based Multifractional Process (GHBMP). Analyses includes estimation of the Hurst function of the multifractional process, clustering multifractional processes based on the Hurst function and functions to get an overview of the process.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: parallel (>= 4.2.2), parallelly (>= 1.37.1), ggplot2 (>= 3.5.1), zoo (>= 1.8-12), matrixStats (>= 1.2.0), proxy, rlang, stats
LazyData: false
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
